        <h1>Privacy Policy for CuttingBoard</h1>
        <p><strong>Last Updated: December 12, 2025</strong></p>

        <h2>1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>CuttingBoard ("I," "my," or "me") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how I handle your data when you use my iOS application.</p>

        <h2>2. Data Collection and Storage</h2>

        <h3>2.1 Personal Data</h3>
        <p>I do not collect, store, or sell your personal data. I do not require you to create an account with me directly.</p>

