        <p>CuttingBoard uses Apple's iCloud and CloudKit services to store your data.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Private Data:</strong> Your pantry items, shopping lists, and private recipes are stored locally on your device and/or in your private iCloud container. I do not have access to this data.</li>
