        </ul>

        <h2>3. User Generated Content</h2>
        <p>By submitting a recipe to the Community section, you acknowledge that:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>The content will be publicly available to other users.</li>
            <li>You have the right to share the content (text and images).</li>
            <li>I reserve the right to remove content that violates my Terms of Use or is reported as inappropriate.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>4. Analytics</h2>
        <p>I do not use third-party analytics services to track your behavior within the app. Apple may provide me with anonymized crash reports and usage statistics if you have opted-in to share such data with developers.</p>

